Package de.emotreco.main.dempster

Class DempsterHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.emotreco.main.dempster.DempsterHandler
  • public class DempsterHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to hold a collection of Measures and allow dempster-shafer-operations. Allows for adding Measures after initialisation with a certain size and accumulation of those measures. Important: there is pretty much no safety-net for misuse! If you screw up and add a measure with the wrong size or something like that you might run into errors
